query:
-- Ver sesiones CAELION activas
SELECT 
  id,
  userId,
  caelionEnabled,
  currentRLD,
  rldStatus,
  interactionCount,
  createdAt,
  updatedAt
FROM caelion_sessions
ORDER BY updatedAt DESC
LIMIT 5;

-- Ver eventos de fricción recientes
SELECT 
  id,
  sessionId,
  type,
  severity,
  context,
  timestamp
FROM caelion_friction_events
ORDER BY timestamp DESC
LIMIT 10;
